ents\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vqk1665702657231.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vqk1665702657231.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vqk1665702657231\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /fil\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify input file name to create and compile the keyboard translation table.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqk1665702657231__section_w2326ab1b5b1_w2327ab1b5_w2328ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqk1665702657231__p_d149192e1_d149193e1_d149194e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/fil</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqk1665702657231__section_w2329ab1b5b3_w2330ab1b5_w2331ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1207471e63\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqk1665702657231__p_d149198e1_d149199e1_d149200e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vel1665702657161.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vel1665702657161.html\" title=\"Compile keyboard translation tables.\">/tra</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqk1665702657231__section_w2332ab1b5b5_w2333ab1b5_w2334ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1207471e79\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqk1665702657231__p_d149204e1_d149205e1_d149206e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/fil</span> sub-switch uses the definitions in <var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var> to create and compile the keyboard translation table TERMFILE for the current language and library. The definitions in <var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var> must have been created with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/key</span> command line switch.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div c